## Provenance of the source documents

`data/gold/` contains Markdown conversions of two public decrees issued by the
Rector of Universitas Lampung:

- **SK No. 2661/UN26/KPT/2025** — undergraduate tuition tariffs (UKT), 2025/2026
- **SK No. 2662/UN26/KPT/2025** — institutional development fee tariffs (IPI), 2025/2026

These are public administrative documents. They are redistributed here in
converted form so that the benchmark is reproducible without re-running PDF
extraction, which would otherwise be an uncontrolled source of variation. The
conversions preserve the tables verbatim; no values were altered. Anyone
reusing them should cite the decrees themselves as the underlying source.

## Third-party model outputs

`results/` contains text generated by third-party language models served via
Groq, DeepInfra, and Together. It is published as measurement data for
scientific reproducibility. Users should consult the relevant providers' and
model licences before repurposing these outputs for other ends, such as
training.
